Gerrit-Client

Interact with the Gerrit code review tool from perl.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Gerrit::Client

You can also look for information at:

    GitHub (report bugs here)
        https://github.com/rohanpm/Gerrit-Client

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Gerrit-Client

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Gerrit-Client

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Gerrit-Client/


